(4, 1, '2016-08-17 17:39:36', '2016-08-17 17:39:36', '<h4 style="text-align: justify;">About Degree Programs and Adult Learning Resources</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Have you ever wondered what college life might be like for you? At University of Kennington,Â you''re able to balance current commitments like a job and family while earning a valuable degree.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Working class time into your busy schedule is easy. Our classes can be taken on Saturdays, or two evenings a week. It is possible to earn up to nine credits every eight weeks. With the appropriate prerequisites, you may earn a degree in three years. And all the credits earned in our degree programs include a perfect balance of theory and practical application courses.<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-192" src="http://kenningtonuniversity.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/asian-pakistani-inian-School-Education-girls-boys-talking-college-students-talking.jpg" alt="asian-pakistani-inian-School-Education-girls-boys-talking-college-students-talking" width="600" height="250" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Our Mission:</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">University of Kennington provides educational opportunities, primarily at the undergraduate level, leading to career enhancement for its multicultural adult learners by offering affordable and accessible education in the fields of business and technology.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The practitioner-led curriculum, building on a strong foundation in general education, utilizes flexible teaching and learning models that recognize, embrace and respond to the complex needs of the university''s students.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">University of Kennington''s programs and learning environment feature personalized education and support services, small classes and campus-based as well as online resources that emphasize collaborative learning in the classroom and through technology. Instruction is delivered by professionally and academically qualified faculty committed to student success, promoting lifelong development and assisting students to balance life and education</p>', 'about us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2016-08-20 07:13:45', '2016-08-20 07:13:45', '', 0, 'http://kenningtonuniversity.co.uk/?page_id=4', 0, 'page', '', 0),
