(50, 1, '2016-08-18 03:17:02', '2016-08-18 03:17:02', 'University of Kennington uses the e University System as its virtual classroom provider. The e University is dynamic software that allows students to access lessons, view and submits assignments and grades, receive feedback from instructors, and interact via discussion boards with other students and faculty. E University also allows students to upload Microsoft Office documents and set up online calendars to remind them of deadlines for assignments, discussion boards, quizzes and tests ensuring a punctual submission\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone wp-image-217 size-full" src="http://kenningtonuniversity.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/virtual-classroom-1.jpg" width="600" height="250" />', 'virtual classroom', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'virtual-classroom', '', '', '2016-08-20 07:27:06', '2016-08-20 07:27:06', '', 12, 'http://kenningtonuniversity.co.uk/?page_id=50', 0, 'page', '', 0),
