(54, 1, '2016-08-18 03:17:39', '2016-08-18 03:17:39', '1.You must have one of the following browers installed on your computer:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Internet Explorer 7 or higher</li>\r\n 	<li>Firefox 2 or higher</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n2.My browser is configured with:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Pop-ups enabled</li>\r\n 	<li>JavaScript enabled</li>\r\n 	<li>AJAX enabled</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n3.I am running one of the following operating systems:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Windows XP</li>\r\n 	<li>Windows Vista</li>\r\n 	<li>Macintosh OS X</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-215" src="http://kenningtonuniversity.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/FreeGreatPicture.com-28696-business-technology-1.jpg" alt="FreeGreatPicture.com-28696-business-technology" width="600" height="250" />\r\n\r\n4.The amount of RAM installed in my computer meets or exceeds my operating system requirements.\r\n\r\n5.My Java Runtime Environment is 1.4 or higher.\r\n\r\n6.I am able to view flash-enabled websites, Windows Media content, Quicktime movies, and PDF documents.\r\n\r\n7.I have Microsoft Word, Excel, and PowerPoint installed (2003 or higher).\r\n\r\n8.My computer is connected to the Internet.', 'technical requirements', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'technical-requirements', '', '', '2016-08-20 07:26:33', '2016-08-20 07:26:33', '', 12, 'http://kenningtonuniversity.co.uk/?page_id=54', 0, 'page', '', 0),
