(98, 1, '2016-08-18 17:45:16', '2016-08-18 17:45:16', 'Edmonton University uses the e University System as its virtual classroom provider. The e University is dynamic software that allows students to access lessons, view and submits assignments and grades, receive feedback from instructors, and interact via discussion boards with other students and faculty. E University also allows students to upload Microsoft Office documents and set up online calendars to remind them of deadlines for assignments, discussion boards, quizzes and tests ensuring a punctual submission\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-97" src="http://kenningtonuniversity.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/virtual_classroom-300x184.gif" alt="virtual_classroom" width="300" height="184" />', 'virtual classroom', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '50-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-18 17:45:16', '2016-08-18 17:45:16', '', 50, 'http://kenningtonuniversity.co.uk/2016/08/18/50-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
