pitality Management</li>\r\n 	<li>Master in Tourism Management</li>\r\n</ul>', 'school of hospitality', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '40-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-01-02 05:04:13', '2017-01-02 05:04:13', '', 40, 'http://kenningtonuniversity.co.uk/2016/08/20/40-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
