(211, 1, '2016-08-20 07:24:55', '2016-08-20 07:24:55', '<h4 style="text-align: justify;">Online Degree Programs</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Worried that sacrificing the face-to-face student-teacher interaction means that you''ll get less of an education?</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">You never have to worry about that with online degree programs from University of Kennington.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-210" src="http://kenningtonuniversity.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/stock-photos-online-higher-education.jpg" alt="stock-photos-online-higher-education" width="600" height="250" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">University of Kennington''s online degree programs are designed and taught by industry professionals. We are dedicated to ensuring that the quality, relevance, and discipline of our online programs are the same as our on-ground programs. The online course presentations are updated regularly, taking into consideration the world''s constant academic evolution in online education.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">If you are unsure about which online degree programs are best for you, please complete the below form to connect with an University of Kennington specialist.</p>', 'online learning', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-20 07:24:55', '2016-08-20 07:24:55', '', 12, 'http://kenningtonuniversity.co.uk/2016/08/20/12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
